{"tid":625543,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我發開口夢既問題好嚴重","createTime":"2018-04-11T14:02:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-15T03:15:51.000Z","uid":83063,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"da8d3345f2fec799326dd911c9341ec7b92dc839","tid":625543,"uid":83063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T14:02:56.000Z","msg":"話說小弟由細到大都係發開口夢既問題<br />\n<br />\n不過係越大越嚴重<br />\n本身自己一個訓都無乜野 <br />\n但近排結左婚  咁床邊就多左個女人<br />\n我老婆話我發開口夢既時間可以同佢對答如流  但我事後完全無印象<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n舉個例 （我老婆同我講翻個對話）我<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：記得拎翻張Receipt  呀  同埋尾數呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：咩Receipt呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：入數Receipt呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：你又發開口夢呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我無發夢呀  做緊野呀！<br />\n然後我會繼續訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為我啲鼻鼾會響翻起     （ 我做銀行的）<br />\n<br />\n琴晚：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：AVGLE 真係好正呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：咩黎架？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我平時睇AV果個網呀！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：你又發開口夢呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：妖你又話我發開口夢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ： 你係咪回味緊啲乜野<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：（鼻鼾聲繼續）<br />\n<br />\n有無咩辦法可以改善   我驚自己有日唔知會講左啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申： 同老婆Share AC"},{"pid":"e2830f0d753870a6cf31b873fe342a01edf7d590","tid":625543,"uid":2263,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T14:03:59.000Z","msg":"發夢都要做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b087c6dece8f0d58d1c8ddfe8aa263bac4a83474","tid":625543,"uid":98431,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T14:08:27.000Z","msg":"其實你依家都發緊夢<br />\n<br />\n醒下啦 你邊有老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb493ba878d373f6643f94454b62c31858f06948","tid":625543,"uid":138138,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T14:10:06.000Z","msg":"AVGLE 真係好正呀？<br />\n咩黎架？<br />\n我平時睇AV果個網呀！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請問這裡有無管理員，為什麼這裡有這麼多限制級、成人內容， <br />\n而沒人監管或移到成人版， <br />\n本來我讓小朋友來貴壇，是嚴禁到成人區， <br />\n以為就此沒問題。 <br />\n怎知道他們來到這裡，看到了那些限制級內容， <br />\n變得心理開始有問題。 <br />\n請趕快妥善處理，否則，我向相關部門投訴。"},{"pid":"97da41958f2cbedd117c030649498767296dac6d","tid":625543,"uid":83063,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"b087c6dece8f0d58d1c8ddfe8aa263bac4a83474","tid":625543,"uid":98431,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T14:08:27.000Z","msg":"其實你依家都發緊夢<br />\n<br />\n醒下啦 你邊有老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T14:11:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/11/221106_1bbdffc527f6f65de4604320974998e9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F11%2F221106_1bbdffc527f6f65de4604320974998e9.png&h=be94b486&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acdade0819ddd4fb64ca4529b7255605b8f38744","tid":625543,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"